'''Gary Visconti''' (born May 10 1945) was an [[United States|American]] [[figure skater]]. He won the gold medal at the [[U.S. Figure Skating Championships]] twice and captured the bronze medal at the [[World Figure Skating Championships]] two times. He currently works as a coach.
